_sText:
Welcome to FY_petrol

Terrorists: Due to the the rising cost of oil, you have invaded a small 
petrol storage plant with the intention of stealing it, 
and then using it to ride on ATV's for hours, just for fun.

Counter-Terrorists: You were some plant workers on your break, 
rehearsing for the broadway adaptation of the movie S.W.A.T. so conveniently,
 you are dressed in full tactical gear. Kick those nasty terrorists out of your factory. 

Fight for control.

Map created by UnPro. 
 
For ClanWarCore UK.

Level Unknown Studios 



This is my 4th release on FPSB, this map was a project for a friend. 
All in all it took 2 light days of work, from concept to upload.

Compile time was less than 3 minutes. 

It is capable of supporting 32 players, however it is a very small map, 
so the more payers, the crazier it will get.
